(Mango Shake team)

853
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:14,130
Okay.

854
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:16,440
Now, we'll start our first competition.

855
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:18,020
Group squat.

856
00:37:18,020 --> 00:37:19,030
Six people per team.

857
00:37:19,030 --> 00:37:21,690
Sit on your teammate's legs
and do the squat.

858
00:37:21,690 --> 00:37:23,450
Then, start the timer at the same time.

859
00:37:23,590 --> 00:37:25,510
Whichever team falls first,

860
00:37:25,510 --> 00:37:27,240
the other team wins.

861
00:37:27,500 --> 00:37:27,990
Come on.

862
00:37:27,990 --> 00:37:29,040
Let's try it first.

863
00:37:29,040 --> 00:37:29,430
Okay.

864
00:37:29,430 --> 00:37:30,400
(Geniuses Strike team)
How's the first?

865
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:31,920
- The first one should be the lightest.
Yeah.

866
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:32,540
(Planning the lineup)
The lightest.

867
00:37:32,540 --> 00:37:33,960
(Strategy: the lightest goes first)
Me?

868
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:35,520
(Strategy: the lightest goes first)
I'll go first.

869
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:36,460
What about you?

870
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:38,590
You're second.

871
00:37:38,590 --> 00:37:39,670
I'm second.

872
00:37:39,670 --> 00:37:40,650
Okay, you're second.

873
00:37:40,650 --> 00:37:41,960
As long as I'm not last.

874
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:43,130
- I'm third.
- Okay.

875
00:37:43,130 --> 00:37:44,430
You're fourth.

876
00:37:44,540 --> 00:37:46,340
- I don't want to be last.
- I'm fifth, you're sixth. How's that?

877
00:37:46,610 --> 00:37:47,200
Okay.

878
00:37:48,200 --> 00:37:49,970
Kai, try opening up a little.

879
00:37:51,010 --> 00:37:51,540
Really?

880
00:37:51,540 --> 00:37:53,280
No, we need to stick together.

881
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,840
Stick together? Then I sit like this?

882
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:56,580
- Like this?
- No.

883
00:37:56,580 --> 00:38:01,050
- Everyone's supposed to squat.
- Then sit down.

884
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:03,640
Don't just sit. You've got to squat too.

885
00:38:03,640 --> 00:38:04,240
Got it.

886
00:38:04,260 --> 00:38:09,630
(Mango Shake team begins to arrange)

887
00:38:09,630 --> 00:38:11,300
We need to figure out
how to get them down first.

888
00:38:11,300 --> 00:38:12,580
(Secretly planning a disruption)

889
00:38:12,580 --> 00:38:13,440
- Go flirt with them.
- Flirt?

890
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:14,880
Flirt with Eugene.

891
00:38:14,900 --> 00:38:15,680
Are you ready?

892
00:38:15,680 --> 00:38:16,410
Ready.

893
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:21,060
Sit down.

894
00:38:21,060 --> 00:38:23,340
Lean forward first.

895
00:38:30,750 --> 00:38:31,840
Someone, go flirt.

896
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:33,690
Cannon, where are you?

897
00:38:33,700 --> 00:38:37,230
Cannon!

898
00:38:37,930 --> 00:38:38,780
What?

899
00:38:38,780 --> 00:38:40,320
Cannon, I miss you!

900
00:38:40,620 --> 00:38:42,370
Lean forward.

901
00:38:42,830 --> 00:38:44,050
What are you doing, Cannon?

902
00:38:44,050 --> 00:38:45,700
I'm singing.

903
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:47,950
Let me hear you sing.

904
00:38:47,950 --> 00:38:51,280
I can't anymore.

905
00:38:51,280 --> 00:38:52,250
So nice.

906
00:38:53,120 --> 00:38:54,060
Aren't we supposed to be squatting?

907
00:38:54,060 --> 00:38:55,470
I feel like I'm really sitting.

908
00:38:55,470 --> 00:38:58,100
(Properly sitting)
Didn't you say everyone squats?

909
00:38:58,330 --> 00:38:59,490
I didn't sit. I'm squatting.

910
00:38:59,660 --> 00:39:02,050
I think Tai's sitting on me.

911
00:39:02,050 --> 00:39:04,170
No, I've got a lot of weight in front.

912
00:39:05,060 --> 00:39:10,640
(Thai team on the other side
is also working hard)

913
00:39:13,490 --> 00:39:15,350
I can help lift you up a bit.

914
00:39:15,840 --> 00:39:18,590
(Don't go back. Don't move)
- Don't move.

915
00:39:18,790 --> 00:39:20,390
Don't move. Don't grab Jony.

916
00:39:20,390 --> 00:39:21,180
Don't grab down there.

917
00:39:21,350 --> 00:39:21,800
What?

918
00:39:22,420 --> 00:39:23,750
What are you saying?

919
00:39:23,750 --> 00:39:26,940
(Hold it in. Crisis starts from within)
That's just...

920
00:39:27,990 --> 00:39:29,520
(Haha)
Don't move.

921
00:39:29,520 --> 00:39:31,070
Quiet.

922
00:39:31,970 --> 00:39:33,330
(Grinds teeth)

923
00:39:33,330 --> 00:39:34,920
Who's grabbing my pants?

924
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:35,930
Stop talking!

925
00:39:37,210 --> 00:39:38,200
Stop laughing.

926
00:39:38,200 --> 00:39:39,710
No laughing. Stop laughing.

927
00:39:39,710 --> 00:39:40,120
(Hold it in)

928
00:39:40,120 --> 00:39:40,740
Ryu.

929
00:39:41,390 --> 00:39:42,100
Cannon!

930
00:39:42,100 --> 00:39:43,720
Ryu's laughing. Tease him.

931
00:39:43,720 --> 00:39:44,920
Call him out. Do the tongue thing.

932
00:39:45,230 --> 00:39:45,860
Tai, go.

933
00:39:45,860 --> 00:39:46,810
Ryu.

934
00:39:47,050 --> 00:39:47,640
What?

935
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:54,970
Ryu.

936
00:40:10,240 --> 00:40:11,840
Thanks to Kai.

937
00:40:12,210 --> 00:40:14,120
He carried the weight of many people.

938
00:40:20,780 --> 00:40:22,760
(Squat, Geniuses Strike team wins)

939
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:24,720
Sharp hat soccer match.

940
00:40:24,860 --> 00:40:26,960
Both sides send two people each round.

941
00:40:26,960 --> 00:40:29,560
Players wear sharp hats
to compete in soccer.

942
00:40:29,560 --> 00:40:31,190
The team that scores first wins.

943
00:40:31,900 --> 00:40:33,220
What's our strategy?

944
00:40:33,220 --> 00:40:35,750
You just go for the ball.

945
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:37,660
He'll take the goal.

946
00:40:37,660 --> 00:40:38,830
(Take the goal to?)
Then you...

947
00:40:38,830 --> 00:40:40,510
(Take the goal to?)
Take the goal?

948
00:40:40,510 --> 00:40:41,800
(Take the goal to?)
Yes, who says we can't?

949
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:43,540
Then you find the goal. I'll find...

950
00:40:43,540 --> 00:40:44,670
Don't point.

951
00:40:44,670 --> 00:40:45,680
You control the ball.

952
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:47,440
When he brings the goal,

953
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:48,570
you just score and end it.

954
00:40:48,570 --> 00:40:49,130
Alright.

955
00:40:49,390 --> 00:40:50,090
So?

956
00:40:51,210 --> 00:40:51,980
What should we do?

957
00:40:55,500 --> 00:40:56,340
Who's going to grab the ball?

958
00:40:57,320 --> 00:41:01,140
One person stays with this.

959
00:41:01,140 --> 00:41:03,500
The other puts the ball by the goal.

960
00:41:03,500 --> 00:41:04,820
By the goal?

961
00:41:04,820 --> 00:41:05,850
Can we put it by the goal?

962
00:41:05,850 --> 00:41:06,340
Forget it.

963
00:41:06,340 --> 00:41:08,050
No rules, so we can do whatever.

964
00:41:08,730 --> 00:41:10,030
One person watch the goal.

965
00:41:10,340 --> 00:41:12,230
Put it in front. Don't let it in.

966
00:41:12,230 --> 00:41:12,910
Okay.

967
00:41:13,340 --> 00:41:14,560
(Sharp Hat Soccer Match, Round 1)
(Kai, U.Jay vs. Deaw, Poom)

968
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:16,760
Alright, ready.

969
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:18,510
Go forward!

970
00:41:18,610 --> 00:41:19,300
(Kicked it)

971
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:21,720
(The ball landed at Kai's feet)

972
00:41:21,720 --> 00:41:22,120
In front.

973
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:23,210
Kai, look ahead!

974
00:41:24,210 --> 00:41:24,930
Where is it?

975
00:41:24,930 --> 00:41:26,820
Right in front.

976
00:41:26,930 --> 00:41:27,880
(Where)
Kai, look ahead!

977
00:41:27,880 --> 00:41:29,540
U.Jay, right side!

978
00:41:29,540 --> 00:41:31,070
(Right side)
Right side!

979
00:41:31,070 --> 00:41:32,250
Yes.

980
00:41:33,250 --> 00:41:33,940
(Perfect miss)

981
00:41:33,940 --> 00:41:34,850
Kai, go forward.

982
00:41:34,850 --> 00:41:35,360
Where is it?

983
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:36,910
Left side, U.Jay, left!

984
00:41:36,910 --> 00:41:38,980
Poom, go forward!

985
00:41:38,980 --> 00:41:41,180
Poom, keep walking, walk, walk.

986
00:41:41,180 --> 00:41:42,830
It's there.

987
00:41:42,830 --> 00:41:43,620
Kick it.

988
00:41:45,410 --> 00:41:46,030
(Missed)

989
00:41:47,240 --> 00:41:49,080
U.Jay, left side!

990
00:41:49,080 --> 00:41:49,840
Right!

991
00:41:52,810 --> 00:41:54,190
Where is it?

992
00:42:00,210 --> 00:42:01,470
(Like a headless fly)

993
00:42:01,600 --> 00:42:02,500
Where'd it go?

994
00:42:02,690 --> 00:42:03,740
Kai, right in front.

995
00:42:03,740 --> 00:42:04,880
Kai, go forward.

996
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:06,170
Straight ahead for both of you.

997
00:42:06,700 --> 00:42:07,260
In front.

998
00:42:07,260 --> 00:42:07,950
Right side.

999
00:42:07,950 --> 00:42:09,330
- Yeah.
- I see it.

1000
00:42:09,880 --> 00:42:11,640
(U.Jay sees the ball)
Kai, grab the goal!

1001
00:42:11,640 --> 00:42:12,710
Grab the goal!

1002
00:42:13,420 --> 00:42:14,900
Kai, get the goal!

1003
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:16,240
Go back.

1004
00:42:16,240 --> 00:42:17,700
(Deaw goes back to guard the goal)
Grab the goal!

1005
00:42:17,700 --> 00:42:18,900
Go!

1006
00:42:18,900 --> 00:42:20,010
(Runs quickly)
Grab it and run!

1007
00:42:20,410 --> 00:42:21,210
(Avoids the obstacle)

1008
00:42:22,020 --> 00:42:23,190
(Kai grabs the goal)
Give it to U.Jay!

1009
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:24,930
U.Jay!

1010
00:42:24,930 --> 00:42:25,630
Where are you?

1011
00:42:25,630 --> 00:42:26,150
U.Jay!

1012
00:42:26,150 --> 00:42:26,870
Where are you?

1013
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:28,970
(Can Deaw and Poom stop them?)

1014
00:42:29,120 --> 00:42:30,570
U.Jay, hurry up!

1015
00:42:32,450 --> 00:42:35,260
(Kai and U.Jay score)

1016
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:45,640
Suddenly, we seem pretty evil.

1017
00:42:49,720 --> 00:42:52,540
They've been controlling the ball.

1018
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:53,770
So?

1019
00:42:55,050 --> 00:42:55,800
Poom,

1020
00:42:56,120 --> 00:42:58,290
go grab their goal and put it here.

1021
00:42:58,290 --> 00:42:59,130
I'll run like this.

1022
00:42:59,130 --> 00:42:59,820
Then...

1023
00:43:01,070 --> 00:43:03,530
Calm down.

1024
00:43:03,960 --> 00:43:06,880
If China team scores again,
this round ends.

1025
00:43:06,880 --> 00:43:08,450
Okay.

1026
00:43:08,450 --> 00:43:08,860
(Round 2)

1027
00:43:08,860 --> 00:43:09,580
(Pippin, Eugene vs. Ryu, Poom)
Ready?

1028
00:43:10,700 --> 00:43:11,440
Ready.

1029
00:43:12,650 --> 00:43:13,940
Okay.

1030
00:43:14,750 --> 00:43:15,470
Come on.

1031
00:43:15,470 --> 00:43:16,230
(Pippin is the first to spot the ball)
Okay.

1032
00:43:16,230 --> 00:43:17,540
Go straight. Be careful.

1033
00:43:17,540 --> 00:43:18,890
(Safety instinct at max)
Go.

1034
00:43:19,180 --> 00:43:19,660
Okay.

1035
00:43:19,660 --> 00:43:20,700
Pippin missed.

1036
00:43:20,700 --> 00:43:21,670
Behind.

1037
00:43:21,840 --> 00:43:23,130
Slowly.

1038
00:43:23,130 --> 00:43:25,100
- Where is it?
- Okay, continue.

1039
00:43:25,100 --> 00:43:25,550
Where is it?

1040
00:43:25,550 --> 00:43:26,500
In front.

1041
00:43:26,500 --> 00:43:28,260
- Continue.
- Go for it.

1042
00:43:28,260 --> 00:43:29,580
Go!

1043
00:43:30,440 --> 00:43:33,120
You missed it.

1044
00:43:35,690 --> 00:43:36,600
Alright.

1045
00:43:37,160 --> 00:43:38,440
(Hugs immediately)

1046
00:43:39,530 --> 00:43:41,870
Wrong direction. Go straight.

1047
00:43:41,880 --> 00:43:44,540
(Caught Poom)

1048
00:43:45,180 --> 00:43:45,950
Go straight.

1049
00:43:46,280 --> 00:43:46,890
Go.

1050
00:43:46,890 --> 00:43:47,780
(And Ryu, who's lost)

1051
00:43:47,930 --> 00:43:52,020
Go.

1052
00:43:52,120 --> 00:43:52,840
Ryu, go straight.

1053
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:54,070
Go straight.

1054
00:43:54,070 --> 00:43:55,370
Right side.

1055
00:43:55,640 --> 00:43:57,140
(Left, right)
Ryu, step back.

1056
00:43:57,140 --> 00:43:59,270
Step back. Go straight. Stop.

1057
00:43:59,270 --> 00:44:00,060
It's right there.

1058
00:44:00,060 --> 00:44:00,710
Go.

1059
00:44:00,710 --> 00:44:02,900
(Ryu successfully grabs the ball)
Don't listen to others. Go straight.

1060
00:44:02,900 --> 00:44:04,050
Grab it. Kick it.

1061
00:44:06,760 --> 00:44:08,790
- Where is it?
- It's gone.

1062
00:44:08,790 --> 00:44:10,710
Director's side!

1063
00:44:10,710 --> 00:44:11,380
(Pull him)
I don't see it.

1064
00:44:11,380 --> 00:44:12,220
Camera side!

1065
00:44:12,220 --> 00:44:12,920
Where is it?

1066
00:44:13,460 --> 00:44:14,430
I don't see it.

1067
00:44:19,440 --> 00:44:20,370
Where did it go?

1068
00:44:24,870 --> 00:44:27,450
Go straight.

1069
00:44:27,600 --> 00:44:28,680
It's on your right.

1070
00:44:29,030 --> 00:44:29,870
Pippin's...

1071
00:44:29,870 --> 00:44:31,050
On Pippin's right!

1072
00:44:31,260 --> 00:44:34,250
Pippin's right!

1073
00:44:34,250 --> 00:44:34,920
Your right!

1074
00:44:36,520 --> 00:44:37,560
(Awesome)

1075
00:44:37,710 --> 00:44:38,450
Did they score?

1076
00:44:38,450 --> 00:44:39,470
(Completely clueless)

1077
00:44:42,770 --> 00:44:43,380
Nice!

1078
00:44:43,380 --> 00:44:45,820
Go forward. Go.

1079
00:44:45,820 --> 00:44:46,520
Go forward.

1080
00:44:46,520 --> 00:44:48,100
He took the ball.

1081
00:44:52,040 --> 00:44:52,830
Keep going.

1082
00:44:52,830 --> 00:44:53,590
Pull him away!

1083
00:44:53,590 --> 00:44:54,610
Pull him away.

1084
00:44:54,610 --> 00:44:55,990
Pull.

1085
00:44:56,500 --> 00:44:57,550
Pull him away.

1086
00:44:57,550 --> 00:44:58,740
Pull.

1087
00:44:59,140 --> 00:44:59,930
No.

1088
00:44:59,930 --> 00:45:04,980
No fighting.

1089
00:45:05,420 --> 00:45:07,670
Let go of him, Eugene.

1090
00:45:07,670 --> 00:45:09,730
Forget about Ryu.

1091
00:45:09,730 --> 00:45:10,460
Wait, move aside.

1092
00:45:10,460 --> 00:45:11,360
Let me jump in.

1093
00:45:13,220 --> 00:45:14,330
(Pippin and Eugene score)

1094
00:45:14,330 --> 00:45:15,260
Got it!

1095
00:45:17,190 --> 00:45:18,770
It's in.

1096
00:45:19,410 --> 00:45:20,040
Did we score?

1097
00:45:20,040 --> 00:45:21,420
(It's a mess)
Yes.

1098
00:45:21,650 --> 00:45:22,630
Goal.

1099
00:45:23,260 --> 00:45:24,270
The goal.

1100
00:45:25,270 --> 00:45:26,340
The goal's broken.

1101
00:45:29,820 --> 00:45:32,310
(Sharp Hat Soccer Match,
Geniuses Strike Team wins)

1102
00:45:32,430 --> 00:45:33,360
Relay race.

1103
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:35,750
The two teams will do a relay race.

1104
00:45:35,750 --> 00:45:36,840
One person carries their teammate.

1105
00:45:36,840 --> 00:45:39,000
After five squats,
touch the second teammate.

1106
00:45:39,260 --> 00:45:40,550
Second teammate spins a hula hoop.

1107
00:45:40,550 --> 00:45:43,260
Feed another teammate an apple
before touching the third teammate.

1108
00:45:43,380 --> 00:45:45,580
For the third leg, two teammates
spin around ten times,

1109
00:45:45,580 --> 00:45:48,300
then touch their fingers together.
After five jump ropes together,

1110
00:45:48,440 --> 00:45:50,210
win the other team

1111
00:45:50,210 --> 00:45:51,130
with rock-paper-scissors.

1112
00:45:51,350 --> 00:45:54,180
If they fail, they start the task again
until they succeed.

1113
00:45:54,180 --> 00:45:55,240
The team

1114
00:45:55,240 --> 00:45:57,070
with the shortest time wins.

1115
00:45:57,200 --> 00:46:00,870
Alright, now let's have
the leading China team go first.

1116
00:46:03,160 --> 00:46:03,930
Good luck!

1117
00:46:04,060 --> 00:46:07,280
Good luck.

1118
00:46:07,580 --> 00:46:08,580
Three, two, one.

1119
00:46:08,580 --> 00:46:10,710
Geniuses strike is unstoppable!

1120
00:46:12,420 --> 00:46:14,720
(Group Relay Race, Geniuses Strike team)
Ready?

1121
00:46:15,410 --> 00:46:17,280
- You go first.
- Your time starts now.

1122
00:46:18,270 --> 00:46:19,900
One, two.

1123
00:46:21,480 --> 00:46:23,120
Four, five.

1124
00:46:23,310 --> 00:46:24,640
Alright, go.

1125
00:46:25,070 --> 00:46:26,360
Touch. Go.

1126
00:46:26,360 --> 00:46:27,030
Take this.

1127
00:46:27,030 --> 00:46:27,840
(Hand off successful)

1128
00:46:27,840 --> 00:46:29,160
Spin it. I'm gonna eat it.

1129
00:46:30,090 --> 00:46:30,840
Spin it.

1130
00:46:31,060 --> 00:46:32,460
Don't move your hands.

1131
00:46:32,460 --> 00:46:33,640
Your hands, don't move.

