1415
00:59:19,760 --> 00:59:21,530
(Shoulder pad fell off)
My shoulder pad.

1416
00:59:21,530 --> 00:59:23,090
(Shoulder pad fell off)
It's buried underneath!

1417
00:59:23,550 --> 00:59:24,270
Cannon!

1418
00:59:24,270 --> 00:59:25,810
(Items scattered everywhere)

1419
00:59:25,810 --> 00:59:26,760
What is this?

1420
00:59:29,740 --> 00:59:30,280
Unbelievable!

1421
00:59:30,350 --> 00:59:32,500
All thanks to Kai!

1422
00:59:34,210 --> 00:59:37,020
This is how Kai did it!

1423
00:59:37,020 --> 00:59:39,400
He stepped on me!

1424
00:59:39,960 --> 00:59:43,400
(Kai lifting the whole time)

1425
00:59:43,400 --> 00:59:44,600
(Lift +1)

1426
00:59:44,600 --> 00:59:46,580
Pull me! It's fine!

1427
00:59:46,580 --> 00:59:47,690
Pull me!

1428
00:59:47,690 --> 00:59:48,640
(Lift +2)

1429
00:59:48,640 --> 00:59:49,580
Hang on a sec!

1430
00:59:49,580 --> 00:59:50,500
I'll switch to another one.

1431
00:59:52,160 --> 00:59:53,240
(Lift +3)

1432
00:59:53,240 --> 00:59:56,130
No need! Let them go first!

1433
00:59:56,130 --> 00:59:57,090
I'll go last!

1434
00:59:57,090 --> 00:59:58,920
(MVP)

1435
00:59:59,330 --> 01:00:00,450
What's the strategy?

1436
01:00:01,620 --> 01:00:03,140
(Sides switch offense/defense)
What's the strategy?

1437
01:00:03,140 --> 01:00:05,410
Maybe we should
just let them pass easily.

1438
01:00:05,410 --> 01:00:08,040
(Don't want to go through that again)

1439
01:00:08,330 --> 01:00:09,250
Let's do this.

1440
01:00:09,250 --> 01:00:10,820
We let the first few pass easily,

1441
01:00:10,820 --> 01:00:12,140
then block the rest hard.

1442
01:00:12,140 --> 01:00:13,560
When Tron passes, just let him go.

1443
01:00:13,560 --> 01:00:14,600
(Target the weak)
Grab the smaller ones.

1444
01:00:14,610 --> 01:00:17,180
(Target the weak)
Catch them all.

1445
01:00:17,180 --> 01:00:17,820
(Target the weak)
Don't let them through.

1446
01:00:17,820 --> 01:00:19,470
Grab their smallest one.

1447
01:00:19,470 --> 01:00:21,800
All six of us grab him.

1448
01:00:21,800 --> 01:00:22,420
Hold him in the middle.

1449
01:00:22,420 --> 01:00:23,800
- Grab Poom.
- Yeah, just lock him down.

1450
01:00:23,800 --> 01:00:25,530
All six of us focus on him.

1451
01:00:25,530 --> 01:00:27,500
We just need to hold Poom.

1452
01:00:27,500 --> 01:00:29,160
If I go first,

1453
01:00:29,160 --> 01:00:29,730
someone will lock me down.

1454
01:00:29,730 --> 01:00:30,260
(Wrong guess)

1455
01:00:30,260 --> 01:00:33,600
I'll lie flat and block them.

1456
01:00:33,600 --> 01:00:34,980
You guys climb over me.

1457
01:00:35,540 --> 01:00:37,920
(Let Tron go first)
No, they'll block you. Let us through.

1458
01:00:37,920 --> 01:00:40,860
(Let Tron go first)
As long as Tron escapes, we're good.

1459
01:00:41,610 --> 01:00:43,220
Round two.

1460
01:00:43,220 --> 01:00:44,220
This is terrifying.

1461
01:00:44,220 --> 01:00:45,680
I'm scared too.

1462
01:00:48,800 --> 01:00:51,920
(Tron charges in)

1463
01:00:51,920 --> 01:00:54,210
Leo, keep going! Stretch out!

1464
01:00:54,210 --> 01:00:55,400
Let him pass!

1465
01:00:55,400 --> 01:00:56,420
(Full-on pressure)
Let him pass!

1466
01:00:58,240 --> 01:00:59,310
That hurts!

1467
01:00:59,310 --> 01:01:00,510
Grab one! Block one!

1468
01:01:00,510 --> 01:01:03,150
Got Ryu!

1469
01:01:03,150 --> 01:01:05,070
That hurts. I can't take it!

1470
01:01:05,940 --> 01:01:07,180
Got him!

1471
01:01:09,120 --> 01:01:10,190
(Tai grabs Ryu
U.Jay & Eugene grab Deaw)

1472
01:01:10,190 --> 01:01:10,670
(Pippin & Kai grab Poom)
Got him!

1473
01:01:10,670 --> 01:01:11,180
(Pippin & Kai grab Poom)
Move!

1474
01:01:11,180 --> 01:01:12,180
(Pippin & Kai grab Poom)
Got him!

1475
01:01:13,440 --> 01:01:14,850
(Three get through)

1476
01:01:16,540 --> 01:01:18,250
Hurry!

1477
01:01:19,720 --> 01:01:20,540
(Locking onto Deaw)

1478
01:01:20,540 --> 01:01:21,310
Oh my god!

1479
01:01:21,470 --> 01:01:22,970
Help me!

1480
01:01:23,470 --> 01:01:24,350
Oh my god!

1481
01:01:26,200 --> 01:01:27,960
(Four get through)

1482
01:01:27,960 --> 01:01:29,180
(Five get through)
Pippin, hurry!

1483
01:01:29,180 --> 01:01:30,930
(Only Deaw left)
Don't move! Stay down!

1484
01:01:30,930 --> 01:01:32,090
(No idea what to do)
Got him!

1485
01:01:32,090 --> 01:01:33,220
Got him!

1486
01:01:33,490 --> 01:01:35,230
Tickle him!

1487
01:01:35,230 --> 01:01:36,700
I'm not ticklish!

1488
01:01:40,530 --> 01:01:41,140
U.Jay!

1489
01:01:43,490 --> 01:01:44,670
This hurts!

1490
01:01:44,670 --> 01:01:46,240
Someone help me!

1491
01:01:47,920 --> 01:01:49,340
Tickle him!

1492
01:01:54,990 --> 01:01:55,790
Tickle him!

1493
01:01:56,990 --> 01:02:00,450
You're not getting away!

1494
01:02:00,450 --> 01:02:01,520
Alright, we won!

1495
01:02:01,520 --> 01:02:03,680
Did we win or not?

1496
01:02:07,220 --> 01:02:08,140
There's more here.

1497
01:02:08,140 --> 01:02:08,930
It's fine. They want to win.

1498
01:02:08,930 --> 01:02:09,850
We need to get out of here.

1499
01:02:10,240 --> 01:02:11,040
Get out!

1500
01:02:11,040 --> 01:02:12,840
(Showing up on their own)
Get out now!

1501
01:02:12,840 --> 01:02:14,120
Out!

1502
01:02:14,930 --> 01:02:16,370
Get out, Tai!

1503
01:02:16,690 --> 01:02:19,230
Okay, let's announce the results.

1504
01:02:20,040 --> 01:02:23,200
(Chinese team: 2 minutes 36 seconds)

1505
01:02:23,200 --> 01:02:24,890
3 minutes 22 seconds.

1506
01:02:29,640 --> 01:02:31,160
(Out of energy)

1507
01:02:33,360 --> 01:02:35,640
(Rolling in the Luck:
Geniuses Strike team wins!)

1508
01:02:37,770 --> 01:02:39,340
As the

1509
01:02:39,340 --> 01:02:40,930
(Serious)
last rays if sunlight fade,

1510
01:02:40,930 --> 01:02:44,720
we're wrapping up today's land games.

1511
01:02:46,490 --> 01:02:47,480
I had a great time.

1512
01:02:48,090 --> 01:02:50,210
Thank you, everyone. Great job today!

1513
01:02:50,210 --> 01:02:51,580
It was really fun and exciting.

1514
01:02:51,580 --> 01:02:53,040
(Looking forward to it)
Can't wait for tomorrow's games.

1515
01:02:53,040 --> 01:02:54,990
We won't be going easy tomorrow.

1516
01:02:54,990 --> 01:02:56,190
I'll give it my all tomorrow.

1517
01:02:56,190 --> 01:02:56,850
Today was amazing.

1518
01:02:56,850 --> 01:02:59,760
And I hope everyone stays safe tomorrow.

1519
01:02:59,760 --> 01:03:02,960
(Safety first)
Also, sorry if anyone got hurt.

1520
01:03:02,960 --> 01:03:05,720
I'm sorry.

1521
01:03:05,720 --> 01:03:07,760
It's okay.

1522
01:03:07,760 --> 01:03:10,010
- How are you, Kai?
- I'm sorry.

1523
01:03:10,010 --> 01:03:11,770
Pay for my new nose, okay?

1524
01:03:12,930 --> 01:03:17,220
I've never competed
against the Chinese team

1525
01:03:17,220 --> 01:03:19,440
in an international match before.

1526
01:03:19,440 --> 01:03:21,850
At first, I felt the pressure.
I'm worried we might lose.

1527
01:03:21,850 --> 01:03:23,550
But after winning,
I could finally smile.

1528
01:03:24,940 --> 01:03:27,180
Honestly,
you should be thanking me.

1529
01:03:27,180 --> 01:03:28,120
Thanks.

1530
01:03:28,120 --> 01:03:30,250
That's it for today.
Let's continue tomorrow.

1531
01:03:30,250 --> 01:03:33,230
Today was so much fun.
I want to keep playing like this.

1532
01:03:33,230 --> 01:03:34,450
I want more games like this.

1533
01:03:36,420 --> 01:03:38,780
How about we end with a hug?

1534
01:03:38,780 --> 01:03:39,900
Hug it out!

1535
01:03:39,900 --> 01:03:42,730
Let's give each other a hug.

1536
01:03:42,730 --> 01:03:45,280
Say what's on your mind.

1537
01:03:45,280 --> 01:03:47,220
We can say,

1538
01:03:47,220 --> 01:03:51,480
"Way To You, Up Up Up!"

1539
01:03:53,970 --> 01:03:57,050
That's it for today's games.

1540
01:03:57,050 --> 01:03:58,780
Don't get discouraged. Keep pushing.

1541
01:03:58,780 --> 01:04:00,730
We've got more competitions tomorrow.

1542
01:04:00,730 --> 01:04:02,610
And they're on water.

1543
01:04:02,610 --> 01:04:03,970
It's going to be challenging.

1544
01:04:03,970 --> 01:04:06,160
See you tomorrow.

1545
01:04:06,160 --> 01:04:08,740
Goodbye.

1546
01:04:12,400 --> 01:04:14,220
(Next episode preview)
A new round of games is coming.

1547
01:04:14,220 --> 01:04:15,300
Let's go!

1548
01:04:15,300 --> 01:04:17,560
Kai, take him down!

1549
01:04:17,560 --> 01:04:18,480
Go for it!

1550
01:04:18,480 --> 01:04:20,460
Seriously, games are serious business.

1551
01:04:20,460 --> 01:04:21,720
We have to win.

1552
01:04:21,720 --> 01:04:23,040
That's scary.

1553
01:04:24,680 --> 01:04:25,720
(Who will claim ultimate victory?)

1554
01:04:25,980 --> 01:04:27,850
Next, everyone will put on blindfolds

1555
01:04:27,850 --> 01:04:29,650
and draw lots to reshuffle teams.

1556
01:04:31,450 --> 01:04:34,300
Honestly,
I didn't think about others' choices.

1557
01:04:34,300 --> 01:04:36,440
I just wanted a change.

1558
01:04:36,440 --> 01:04:37,370
And then I...

1559
01:04:37,370 --> 01:04:38,510
He didn't pick me.

1560
01:04:38,510 --> 01:04:40,280
I felt a little disappointed.

1561
01:04:40,280 --> 01:04:41,730
He didn't pick me either.

1562
01:04:41,730 --> 01:04:42,920
That was unexpected.

1563
01:04:42,920 --> 01:04:44,200
Honestly, I just wanted to go solo.

1564
01:04:44,200 --> 01:04:45,480
I'm fine either way.

1565
01:04:46,120 --> 01:04:47,200
(Reshuffling teams
brings new challenges)

1566
01:04:47,200 --> 01:04:50,990
All participants will
face an evaluation on February 22.

1567
01:04:50,990 --> 01:04:52,050
Time is tight.

1568
01:04:52,050 --> 01:04:53,150
It's definitely challenging.

1569
01:04:53,970 --> 01:04:54,620
We're not familiar enough yet.

1570
01:04:54,620 --> 01:04:56,670
Within this limited time,

1571
01:04:56,670 --> 01:04:57,780
we need to push ourselves
to get up to speed.

1572
01:04:57,780 --> 01:04:59,330
I can't feel your energy.

1573
01:04:59,330 --> 01:04:59,870
Disappointed.

1574
01:04:59,870 --> 01:05:01,100
Not up to expectations.

1575
01:05:02,460 --> 01:05:03,650
We didn't perform well.

1576
01:05:03,650 --> 01:05:04,450
This is exhausting.

1577
01:05:04,450 --> 01:05:06,050
I'm leaving. I'm not singing anymore.

1578
01:05:06,050 --> 01:05:07,520
Do you know where Jony is?

1579
01:05:07,520 --> 01:05:08,240
No idea.

1580
01:05:08,240 --> 01:05:09,180
I'm out.

1581
